RECONSIDERATION DOCKET

94-2593. State v. Palmer. Franklin County, No. 87AP-21.

Reported at 72 Ohio St.3d 1536, 650 N.E.2d 477. IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion for reconsideration of this court’s dismissal for want of prosecution be, and is hereby, denied, effective June 29, 1995.
